---
import DashboardLayout from '../../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro';
---

<DashboardLayout title="Ma carte — Fidelopass" activeNav="carte">
  <div class="mb-8 grid gap-4 xl:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] xl:items-end">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-sky-600/70">Studio de création</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Créez une carte fidèle à votre commerce</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">On avance étape par étape : identité, programme, messages, apparence, géolocalisation, puis publication. Vous pouvez revenir en arrière à tout moment sans perdre le fil.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-sky-100 bg-white/90 px-5 py-4 shadow-[0_24px_60px_-42px_rgba(59,130,246,0.45)]">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sky-600/70">Objectif</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Mettre en ligne une carte claire, belle et facile à utiliser en caisse.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Quand tout est prêt, on vous guide automatiquement vers le scanner du personnel puis vers le partage client.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="setup-banner" class="hidden mb-6 rounded-[1.6rem] border border-sky-200 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-50 to-white px-5 py-4 shadow-[0_24px_50px_-38px_rgba(14,165,233,0.35)]">
    <p class="font-medium text-sky-800">Dernière étape de l’onboarding</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
      Vous êtes maintenant dans l’éditeur complet. Créez votre première carte avec toutes les options de personnalisation, puis partagez son lien public à vos clients.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-6 rounded-[2rem] border border-sky-100 bg-white/95 p-5 shadow-[0_30px_80px_-55px_rgba(59,130,246,0.55)]">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-sky-600/70">Parcours guidé</p>
        <h2 class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Configurez votre carte étape par étape</h2>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Le parcours avance dans l’ordre le plus simple : on choisit d’abord une base visuelle, puis on règle le programme, les messages, l’apparence et la proximité avant de publier.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sky-900 shadow-inner">
        <span class="font-semibold" id="wizard-current-label">Étape 1</span>
        <span class="text-slate-500"> sur 8</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-5 grid gap-2 md:grid-cols-4 xl:grid-cols-4 2xl:grid-cols-8">
      {[
        'Type',
        'Identité',
        'Programme',
        'Apparence',
        'Messages',
        'Options',
        'Relecture',
        'Partage',
      ].map((label, index) => (
        <button
          type="button"
          class="wizard-tab rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-white px-3 py-3 text-left transition-all hover:border-sky-200 hover:bg-sky-50"
          data-step-target={String(index + 1)}
        >
          <p class="text-[0.68rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sky-500/80">Étape {index + 1}</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">{label}</p>
        </button>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="public-link-banner" class="wizard-section step-8 hidden mb-6 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-5 py-4 shadow-[0_18px_40px_-34px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)] flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <div>
      <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm font-medium">Votre carte est publiée ✓</p>
      <p id="public-link-url" class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5"></p>
    </div>
    <button id="copy-link-btn" class="shrink-0 rounded-xl bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-emerald-700">Copier le lien</button>
  </div>

  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_370px] gap-6 items-start">

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">

      <!-- Étape 1 : Type de programme -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-1 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Type de programme</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Choisissez d’abord la mécanique de fidélité — tampons ou points. Tout le reste s’adapte à ce choix.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
          <label id="type-tampons-label" class="cursor-pointer rounded-2xl border-2 p-4 transition-all" style="border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255)">
            <input type="radio" name="type" value="tampons" class="hidden" checked />
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-100 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-700">TM</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 text-sm">Tampons</div>
                <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Simple à comprendre, rapide à utiliser en caisse.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </label>
          <label id="type-points-label" class="cursor-pointer rounded-2xl border-2 p-4 transition-all" style="border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff">
            <input type="radio" name="type" value="points" class="hidden" />
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-700">PT</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 text-sm">Points</div>
                <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Plus souple pour les paliers VIP et les récompenses progressives.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
          <label class="label mb-3 block">Formules prêtes à l’emploi</label>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            {[
              {label:’10 achats = 1 offert’, type:’tampons’, total:’10’, reward:’1 produit offert’, points:’100’, perEuro:’1’},
              {label:’8 visites = cadeau’, type:’tampons’, total:’8’, reward:’1 cadeau fidélité’, points:’100’, perEuro:’1’},
              {label:’1€ = 1 point’, type:’points’, total:’10’, reward:’5€ de réduction’, points:’100’, perEuro:’1’},
              {label:’2€ = 1 point’, type:’points’, total:’10’, reward:’10€ de réduction’, points:’200’, perEuro:’0.5’},
              {label:’VIP rapide’, type:’tampons’, total:’5’, reward:’1 avantage VIP’, points:’100’, perEuro:’1’},
              {label:’Récompense premium’, type:’points’, total:’10’, reward:’1 récompense premium’, points:’500’, perEuro:’1’},
            ].map((preset) => (
              <button
                type="button"
                class="program-preset-btn rounded-xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/60 px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs text-slate-600 transition-all hover:border-sky-200 hover:bg-white"
                data-type={preset.type}
                data-total={preset.total}
                data-reward={preset.reward}
                data-points={preset.points}
                data-per-euro={preset.perEuro}
              >
                {preset.label}
              </button>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between gap-3 mb-5">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Modèles rapides</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Choisissez une base prête à l’emploi. Le modèle remplit les couleurs, le programme et le ton général, puis vous l’affinez à votre rythme.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="w-fit rounded-full border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-emerald-700">Recommandé pour démarrer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
          {[
            {name:'Café cosy', badge:'CF', fond:'#2b1608', texte:'#fff7ed', accent:'#d97706', fond2:'#5f3214', pattern:'waves', layout:'bottom', stamp:'☕', type:'tampons', total:'10', reward:'1 boisson offerte', label:'Client', desc:'10 passages = 1 boisson offerte', message:'Votre café vous attend !'},
            {name:'Restaurant', badge:'RS', fond:'#111827', texte:'#fff7ed', accent:'#f97316', fond2:'#7c2d12', pattern:'diagonal', layout:'top', stamp:'🍽️', type:'tampons', total:'8', reward:'1 dessert offert', label:'Table fidèle', desc:'Cumulez des tampons à chaque repas', message:'Une récompense vous attend au restaurant.'},
            {name:'Institut beauté', badge:'BE', fond:'#4a102a', texte:'#fff1f2', accent:'#f472b6', fond2:'#831843', pattern:'confetti', layout:'bottom', stamp:'✨', type:'tampons', total:'6', reward:'-20% sur un soin', label:'Cliente', desc:'Votre carte privilège beauté', message:'Votre avantage beauté est disponible.'},
            {name:'Barber shop', badge:'BR', fond:'#0f172a', texte:'#f8fafc', accent:'#38bdf8', fond2:'#1e3a8a', pattern:'grid', layout:'top', stamp:'✂️', type:'tampons', total:'8', reward:'1 coupe offerte', label:'Client', desc:'Une coupe offerte après 8 passages', message:'Votre barber vous attend.'},
            {name:'Boutique premium', badge:'BT', fond:'#030712', texte:'#fefce8', accent:'#d4af37', fond2:'#422006', pattern:'dots', layout:'background', stamp:'🛍️', type:'points', total:'10', reward:'10€ de réduction', label:'Membre', desc:'Cumulez des points à chaque achat', message:'Votre avantage fidélité est disponible en boutique.'},
            {name:'Sport & coaching', badge:'SP', fond:'#022c22', texte:'#ecfdf5', accent:'#22c55e', fond2:'#064e3b', pattern:'diagonal', layout:'background', stamp:'🏆', type:'points', total:'10', reward:'1 séance offerte', label:'Athlète', desc:'Transformez vos visites en récompenses', message:'Votre coach vous attend.'},
          ].map((preset) => (
            <button
              type="button"
              class="business-template-btn text-left rounded-[1.4rem] border border-sky-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50/60 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-sky-200 hover:shadow-[0_24px_55px_-36px_rgba(59,130,246,0.45)]"
              data-name={preset.name}
              data-icon={preset.badge}
              data-fond={preset.fond}
              data-texte={preset.texte}
              data-accent={preset.accent}
              data-fond2={preset.fond2}
              data-pattern={preset.pattern}
              data-layout={preset.layout}
              data-stamp={preset.stamp}
              data-type={preset.type}
              data-total={preset.total}
              data-reward={preset.reward}
              data-label={preset.label}
              data-desc={preset.desc}
              data-message={preset.message}
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-100 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.12em] text-sky-700">{preset.badge}</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">{preset.name}</p>
                  <p class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-slate-500">{preset.reward}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 h-10 rounded-xl border border-sky-100" style={`background:linear-gradient(135deg,${preset.fond},${preset.fond2})`}>
                <div class="h-full w-1/3 rounded-l-xl" style={`background:${preset.accent}`}></div>
              </div>
            </button>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Étape 2 : Identité -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-2 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Identité visuelle</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Ajoutez les éléments qui feront reconnaître votre commerce au premier coup d’œil : nom, logo et icône de tampon.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-5">
          <div><label class="label" for="nom-carte">Nom de la carte *</label><input id="nom-carte" type="text" class="input" placeholder="Carte fidélité Ma Boutique" required /></div>
          <div><label class="label" for="label-client">Label membre</label><input id="label-client" type="text" class="input" placeholder="Client, Membre, VIP..." maxlength="30" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5"><label class="label" for="description">Description</label><input id="description" type="text" class="input" placeholder="Cumulez des points à chaque achat !" /></div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">

          <div>
            <label class="label mb-2 block">Logo</label>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
              <div id="logo-preview-wrap" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 overflow-hidden" style="background:#1e293b">
                <img id="logo-preview-img" class="hidden w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <span id="logo-preview-icon" class="text-2xl text-slate-500">🏪</span>
              </div>
              <input type="file" id="logo-file" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/webp" class="hidden" />
              <button type="button" id="logo-btn" class="btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-3 w-full">Choisir</button>
              <button type="button" id="logo-palette-btn" class="btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-3 w-full text-emerald-300">Générer une palette</button>
              <input type="hidden" id="logo-url" />
              <p id="logo-loading" class="hidden text-indigo-400 text-xs">Upload...</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs text-center leading-tight">
                PNG/JPG carré<br/>
                Recommandé : 512×512 px<br/>
                Sujet centré, peu de texte, marges fines
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="tampon-icon-section">
            <label class="label mb-2 block">Icône de tampon</label>
            <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-3">
              <label id="tampon-mode-default-label" class="flex-1 cursor-pointer rounded-xl border-2 p-2 text-center transition-all" style="border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255);color:#0f172a">
                <input type="radio" name="tampon_mode" value="default" class="hidden" checked /><div class="text-base mb-0.5">✓</div><div class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-900">Défaut</div>
              </label>
              <label id="tampon-mode-emoji-label" class="flex-1 cursor-pointer rounded-xl border-2 p-2 text-center transition-all" style="border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff">
                <input type="radio" name="tampon_mode" value="emoji" class="hidden" /><div class="text-base mb-0.5">😀</div><div class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-900">Emoji</div>
              </label>
              <label id="tampon-mode-custom-label" class="flex-1 cursor-pointer rounded-xl border-2 p-2 text-center transition-all" style="border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff">
                <input type="radio" name="tampon_mode" value="custom" class="hidden" /><div class="text-base mb-0.5">🖼️</div><div class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-900">Image</div>
              </label>
            </div>
            <div id="tampon-emoji-zone" class="hidden">
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5">Sélectionnez un emoji</p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-1">
                {['☕','🍩','⭐','🎁','❤️','🏆','🍕','🎫','💎','🔥','🎉','✨','🍦','🥐','🛍️','🌟','🎵','🍰','🍽️','✂️','💅','🏋️'].map(e => (
                  <button type="button" class="emoji-stamp-btn w-9 h-9 rounded-lg text-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-transparent" data-emoji={e}>{e}</button>
                ))}
              </div>
              <input type="hidden" id="tampon-emoji" />
              <p id="tampon-emoji-selected" class="hidden text-xs text-indigo-400 mt-1.5">Sélectionné : <span id="tampon-emoji-val"></span></p>
            </div>
            <div id="tampon-custom-zone" class="hidden flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 overflow-hidden" style="background:#1e293b">
                <img id="tampon-preview-img" class="hidden w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" />
                <span id="tampon-preview-icon" class="text-xl text-slate-500">🔖</span>
              </div>
              <input type="file" id="tampon-file" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/webp" class="hidden" />
              <button type="button" id="tampon-btn" class="btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-3 w-full">Choisir image</button>
              <input type="hidden" id="tampon-icon-url" />
              <p id="tampon-loading" class="hidden text-indigo-400 text-xs">Upload...</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs text-center leading-tight">PNG transparent — 64×64 px</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Étape 3 : Programme -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-3 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Programme fidélité</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Définissez l’objectif de fidélité, la récompense principale et les paliers optionnels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div id="config-tampons"><label class="label" for="tampons-total">Nombre de tampons pour la récompense</label><input id="tampons-total" type="number" class="input w-32" min="1" max="20" value="10" /></div>
          <div id="config-points" class="hidden flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div><label class="label" for="points-par-euro">Points / euro</label><input id="points-par-euro" type="number" class="input" min="0.1" step="0.1" value="1" /></div>
              <div><label class="label" for="points-recompense">Points pour la récompense</label><input id="points-recompense" type="number" class="input" min="1" value="100" /></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div><label class="label" for="recompense">Récompense offerte *</label><input id="recompense" type="text" class="input" placeholder="Ex: 1 café offert, 5€ de réduction..." required /></div>
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/60 p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Récompenses multiples</p>
                  <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Ex : café offert au 5e tampon, -10% au 10e.</p>
                </div>
                <button id="add-reward-tier" type="button" class="btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-3">Ajouter</button>
              </div>
              <div id="reward-tiers" class="flex flex-col gap-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="vip-tiers-card" class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-white p-4">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Paliers VIP points</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5 mb-3">Visible surtout pour les programmes à points.</p>
              <div id="vip-tiers" class="flex flex-col gap-2"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Étape 4 : Apparence -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-4 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Apparence</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Choisissez un thème, une palette, une bannière et un fond qui correspondent à votre univers. L’aperçu à droite se met à jour en direct.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="label mb-3 block">Thèmes prédéfinis</label>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-6 gap-2 mb-5">
          {[
            {name:’Nuit’,fond:’#0f172a’,texte:’#ffffff’,accent:’#6366f1’,fond2:’’},
            {name:’Rose’,fond:’#3d0d1e’,texte:’#fce7f3’,accent:’#ec4899’,fond2:’#6d1439’},
            {name:’Forêt’,fond:’#064e3b’,texte:’#ffffff’,accent:’#34d399’,fond2:’#065f46’},
            {name:’Océan’,fond:’#0c4a6e’,texte:’#ffffff’,accent:’#38bdf8’,fond2:’#075985’},
            {name:’Café’,fond:’#1c0e04’,texte:’#fef3c7’,accent:’#d97706’,fond2:’#292200’},
            {name:’Noir’,fond:’#000000’,texte:’#ffffff’,accent:’#8b5cf6’,fond2:’#18003a’},
          ].map(({name,fond,texte,accent,fond2})=>(
            <button type="button" class="preset-btn flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5 rounded-xl border border-sky-100 bg-white p-2 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-sky-200 hover:shadow-[0_18px_40px_-28px_rgba(59,130,246,0.35)]" data-fond={fond} data-texte={texte} data-accent={accent} data-fond2={fond2}>
              <div class="w-full h-8 rounded-lg flex gap-1 p-1" style={fond2?`background:linear-gradient(135deg,${fond},${fond2})`:`background:${fond}`}>
                <div class="w-3 h-full rounded-sm" style={`background:${accent}`}></div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-full rounded-sm opacity-60" style={`background:${texte}`}></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">{name}</span>
            </button>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <label class="label">Couleur de fond</label>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-400">
              <span>Uni</span>
              <button id="gradient-toggle" type="button" class="w-10 h-5 rounded-full transition-all relative" style="background:#334155" aria-pressed="false">
                <span id="gradient-knob" class="absolute top-0.5 left-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-white transition-all"></span>
              </button>
              <span>Dégradé</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-3">
            <div><label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block" id="fond-label">Fond</label><input id="couleur-fond" type="color" value="#0f172a" class="w-full h-10 rounded-xl border border-white/10 cursor-pointer bg-transparent" /></div>
            <div id="fond2-wrap" class="hidden"><label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Fond 2</label><input id="couleur-fond-2" type="color" value="#6366f1" class="w-full h-10 rounded-xl border border-white/10 cursor-pointer bg-transparent" /></div>
            <div><label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Texte</label><input id="couleur-texte" type="color" value="#ffffff" class="w-full h-10 rounded-xl border border-white/10 cursor-pointer bg-transparent" /></div>
            <div><label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Accent</label><input id="couleur-accent" type="color" value="#6366f1" class="w-full h-10 rounded-xl border border-white/10 cursor-pointer bg-transparent" /></div>
          </div>
          <div id="gradient-angle-wrap" class="hidden mt-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1"><label class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Angle du dégradé</label><span id="gradient-angle-val" class="text-indigo-400 text-xs font-mono">135°</span></div>
            <input id="gradient-angle" type="range" min="0" max="360" value="135" class="w-full accent-indigo-500" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <button type="button" id="pattern-toggle" class="flex w-full items-center justify-between rounded-xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/60 px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-sky-100">
            <span>Pattern de la bannière</span>
            <span id="pattern-arrow" class="text-slate-400 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </button>
          <div id="pattern-panel" class="hidden mt-2 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            {[{value:’none’,label:’Aucun’},{value:’dots’,label:’Points’},{value:’grid’,label:’Grille’},{value:’waves’,label:’Vagues’},{value:’diagonal’,label:’Diagonales’},{value:’confetti’,label:’Confetti’}].map(({value,label})=>(
              <label id={`pat-${value}-label`} class="cursor-pointer rounded-xl border-2 p-2.5 text-center transition-all" style={value===’none’?’border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255);color:#0f172a’:’border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff’}>
                <input type="radio" name="pattern_type" value={value} class="hidden" checked={value===’none’} />
                <div class="w-full h-8 rounded-lg mb-1.5 overflow-hidden relative" style="background:#1e293b">
                  {value===’dots’&&<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"><defs><pattern id="pd" width="8" height="8" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="1.5" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.5)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#pd)"/></svg>}
                  {value===’grid’&&<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"><defs><pattern id="pg" width="8" height="8" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 8 0 L 0 0 0 8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(99,102,241,0.4)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#pg)"/></svg>}
                  {value===’waves’&&<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"><defs><pattern id="pw" width="16" height="8" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 0 4 Q 4 0 8 4 Q 12 8 16 4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(99,102,241,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#pw)"/></svg>}
                  {value===’diagonal’&&<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"><defs><pattern id="pdiag" width="8" height="8" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse" patternTransform="rotate(35)"><rect width="2" height="8" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.42)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#pdiag)"/></svg>}
                  {value===’confetti’&&<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"><circle cx="18%" cy="30%" r="3" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.55)"/><rect x="58%" y="18%" width="14" height="4" rx="2" transform="rotate(20)" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.45)"/><circle cx="72%" cy="72%" r="2.5" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.6)"/><rect x="22%" y="70%" width="12" height="4" rx="2" transform="rotate(-25)" fill="rgba(99,102,241,0.4)"/></svg>}
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-900">{label}</div>
              </label>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 mb-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Bannière</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="w-full h-16 rounded-xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center relative" style="background:#1e293b">
              <img id="strip-preview-img" class="hidden w-full h-full object-cover" style="object-position:center" />
              <span id="strip-preview-icon" class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Aucune image</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-1.5">
              <input type="file" id="strip-file" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/webp" class="hidden" />
              <button type="button" id="strip-btn" class="btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-3 flex-1">Choisir</button>
              <button type="button" id="strip-clear" class="hidden btn-secondary text-xs py-1.5 px-2 text-red-400">✕</button>
            </div>
            <input type="hidden" id="strip-url" />
            <p id="strip-loading" class="hidden text-indigo-400 text-xs">Upload...</p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs text-center">PNG/JPG — <strong class="text-slate-500">750×246 px</strong></p>
            <a href="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
              download="template-banniere-fidelopass.svg" class="text-indigo-400 text-xs underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-indigo-300 text-center">⬇ Template SVG 750×246</a>
            <div>
              <label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Style de la bannière</label>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-1.5">
                <label id="strip-style-rounded-label" class="cursor-pointer rounded-lg border-2 py-1.5 text-center text-xs transition-all" style="border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff;color:#64748b">
                  <input type="radio" name="strip_style" value="rounded" class="hidden" />⬜ Arrondi</label>
                <label id="strip-style-full-label" class="cursor-pointer rounded-lg border-2 py-1.5 text-center text-xs transition-all" style="border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255);color:#0f172a">
                  <input type="radio" name="strip_style" value="full" class="hidden" checked />▬ Pleine largeur</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Placement bannière / tampons</label>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1.5">
                {[
                  { value: ‘background’, label: ‘Fond’ },
                  { value: ‘top’, label: ‘Haut’ },
                  { value: ‘bottom’, label: ‘Bas’ },
                ].map(({ value, label }) => (
                  <label id={`strip-layout-${value}-label`} class="cursor-pointer rounded-lg border-2 py-1.5 text-center transition-all text-xs"
                    style={value===’background’?’border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255);color:#0f172a’:’border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff;color:#64748b’}>
                    <input type="radio" name="strip_layout" value={value} class="hidden" checked={value===’background’} />
                    {label}
                  </label>
                ))}
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs mt-1 leading-tight">"Bas" place la bannière sous les tampons dans l’image Wallet générée.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="strip-position-zone" class="hidden">
              <label class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-1.5 block">Position de l’image</label>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1.5">
                {[‘top’,’center’,’bottom’].map(pos => (
                  <label id={`strip-pos-${pos}-label`} class="cursor-pointer rounded-lg border-2 py-1.5 text-center transition-all text-xs"
                    style={pos===’center’?’border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255);color:#0f172a’:’border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff;color:#64748b’}>
                    <input type="radio" name="strip_position" value={pos} class="hidden" checked={pos===’center’} />
                    {pos===’top’?’Haut’:pos===’center’?’Centre’:’Bas’}
                  </label>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Code-barres</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
            {[{value:’QR’,label:’QR Code’,tag:’QR’,desc:’Recommandé’},{value:’PDF417’,label:’Code-barres’,tag:’B1’,desc:’Linéaire’},{value:’AZTEC’,label:’Aztec’,tag:’AZ’,desc:’Compact’},{value:’NONE’,label:’Aucun’,tag:’--’,desc:’Sans code’}].map(({value,label,tag,desc})=>(
              <label id={`barcode-${value.toLowerCase()}-label`} class="cursor-pointer rounded-2xl border-2 p-3 text-center transition-all" style={value===’QR’?’border-color:#60a5fa;background:rgb(239 246 255)’:’border-color:#dbeafe;background:#ffffff’}>
                <input type="radio" name="barcode_type" value={value} class="hidden" checked={value===’QR’} />
                <div class="mx-auto mb-2 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-100 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-700">{tag}</div>
                <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 text-xs">{label}</div><div class="text-slate-500 text-xs">{desc}</div>
              </label>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Étape 5 : Messages -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-5 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Messages client</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Préparez les textes visibles par vos clients au moment de la création et après l’ajout dans Wallet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label class="label" for="welcome-message">Texte d’accueil public</label>
            <input id="welcome-message" type="text" class="input" maxlength="180" placeholder="Bienvenue chez ..., créez votre carte fidélité en 10 secondes." />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="label" for="success-message">Message après ajout Wallet</label>
            <input id="success-message" type="text" class="input" maxlength="180" placeholder="Votre carte est prête, montrez-la à chaque passage." />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Étape 6 : Options -->
      <div class="card wizard-section step-6 p-6">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-slate-900">Options</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Activez la géolocalisation pour faire remonter la carte en boutique, et récompensez les avis Google de vos clients.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Toggle Géolocalisation -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/40 p-4 mb-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-3">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Géolocalisation</p>
